sp-memusage (1.0.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * Mem-monitor-smaps shows now memory usage changes in addition to
    totals.
  * Argument checking improvements in mem-monitor-smaps
  * Fixes: NB#84258

 -- Eero Tamminen <eero.tamminen@nokia.com>  Tue, 15 Apr 2008 16:59:08 +0300

sp-memusage (1.0.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * New helper script (run-with-memusage) has been added.
  * Made naming of existing helper scripts more consistent:
    memusage -> mem- monitor,
    proc-memusage -> mem-monitor-proc,
    sum-smaps-private -> mem-smaps-private,
    sum-dirty-code-pages -> mem-dirty-code-pages
  * Fixes: NB#82164

 -- Eero Tamminen <eero.tamminen@nokia.com>  Thu, 20 Mar 2008 12:45:22 +0200

